CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_ADDRESS_SUBTYPE
/* Generated on 20-JAN-15 03.39.38.165518000 PM -06:00 */
AS

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,address_subtype_cd IN VARCHAR2
,address_subtype_desc IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_address_subtype.add, parms=' || address_subtype_cd || '|' || address_subtype_desc || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_address_subtype a
(
a.address_subtype_cd
,a.address_subtype_desc
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
add.address_subtype_cd
,add.address_subtype_desc
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_address_subtype.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE del (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,address_subtype_cd IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_address_subtype.del, parms=' || address_subtype_cd || '|' || audit_user || '|');
UPDATE chtr.t_address_subtype a
SET a.record_stat = 'D'
,a.modified_dttm = SYSTIMESTAMP
,a.modified_by = del.audit_user
WHERE a.address_subtype_cd = del.address_subtype_cd
;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_address_subtype.del');

END del;

END da_address_subtype;
